    "body": "This is a chown permission error. Since the Makefile was executed as a non-root user, the folder created is owned by that user. Therefore, the script will not be able to chown that folder to another user. Only root is allowed to do that. I have not ran the Makefile myself, but the hint above should get you further. Maybe try running the Makefile with root permissions, ie either as root or sudo.",
